ABSTRACT
Methods and apparatus for providing wireless communica-
tions using subframe partitioning are disclosed. Two or more
base stations may be allocated subframes in a radio frame.
All or part of the subframe allocation may be provided to the
associated user equipment (UES), which may use it to
determine signal metrics during assigned subframes for an
associated base station.
